<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[٨]</span> بَابٌ كَرَاهَةُ نَتْفِ الشَّيْبِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٩٢-<span class="c5"> أَخْبَرَنَا عَبْدُ اللَّهِ بْنُ أَحْمَدَ بْنِ حَنْبَلٍ قَالَ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">سَمِعْتُ أَبِي فِي حَدِيثِ عَبْدِ اللَّهِ بْنِ مَسْعُودٍ ذَكَرَهُ النَّبِيُّ صَلَّى اللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">خَمْسُ خِصَالٍ:</span> تَغْيِيرُ الشَّيْبِ وَنَتْفُ الشَّيْبِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>⦗١٢٩⦘<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ أَبِي:</span> فَسَّرَ لَنَا جَرِيرُ بْنُ عَبْدِ الْحَمِيدِ الرَّاوِيُّ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>